{"id": 2969, "genre": 1000, "title": "生活中的哪些购物决策，会让你觉得“自己长大成人了”？", "description": "买 or 不买哪些东西最能给你带来“成年/独立”的感觉？（题图来自：iStock ©️ CSA-Printstock）", "record_count": 0, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190527151219q5B2DvipHAL6x0we.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "1970-01-01T00:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 5862, "title": "生活中的哪些购物决策，会让你觉得“自己长大成人了”？", "content": "生活中的哪些购物决策，会让你觉得“自己已经成年了”？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 345691, "content": "洗衣机/吸尘器，有一种“我很会照顾自己”的成就感", "image": "img/option/option/20190527161801kqh13rOIs2SJwTMW.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 345692, "content": "囤了一箱小甜酒，可以自己决定啥时候小酌一杯", "image": "img/option/option/20190527162255XZQ97yGpqJ65S8ma.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 345694, "content": "房子/车子之类大件商品，有种成家立业的郑重感", "image": "img/option/option/20190527161942qCJrIEyhlpjGoTDk.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 345696, "content": "一个人租的房子，“一个人住就是独立的开始”", "image": "img/option/option/20190527162520KLWNg2PFc3ndEymV.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 345700, "content": "工作后买的体检套餐，“终于到了需要养生的年纪”", "image": "img/option/option/20190527161630Y8L1EA7cK9FuqZmV.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 345702, "content": "股票/基金之类的投资，“从此也是懂赚钱的人了”", "image": "img/option/option/20190527162550kepjsRf81mJqclXg.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 345705, "content": "全套游戏/手办/漫画，“总算能自己为爱好买单了”", "image": "img/option/option/20190527161748DweApVNZPiB7RQLr.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 345715, "content": "绿植/宠物用品，有一种“年纪轻轻就当了爸妈”的体验", "image": "img/option/option/20190527161737J8eW0Mf2q3AGKF6b.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 345718, "content": "超市/菜市场买菜，表示自己真的很会居家过日子", "image": "img/option/option/20190527155912SADNUROc7VFBLqPT.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}